701399f-a.title: Bronx: Leland Avenue - Westchester Avenue
701399f-a.text:
Leland Avenue, at, and adjoining the N.E. corner of Westchester
Avenue. The corner site is an empty lot, and the 3-story house
adjoining it bears No. 1310 Leland Avenue.
April 10, 1938.
P. L. Sperr.
NO REPRODUCTIONS.
